        <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;使用debian11在本地配置lamp架构的web应用组和typecho博客框架&#34;&gt;使用debian11在本地配置lamp架构的web应用组和typecho博客框架&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;先知&#34;&gt;先知&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、what is the lamp?&lt;br&gt;
lamp is Linux, Apache, Mariadb and Php/Perl/Python.&lt;br&gt;
2、what is typecho?&lt;br&gt;
Typecho is a light and efficient website frame.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;debian11there-are-two-options-to-chooes&#34;&gt;debian11(There are two options to chooes.)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;install debian11 on your PC&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;purchase a VPS and a domain&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
