&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;haven&lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;t set the root password yet, you should just press enter here.
